  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Align Tool</phrase>
    <phrase lang="it">Lo strumento di allineamento</phrase>
  </title>

  <indexterm lang="en"><primary>Align</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Tools</primary><secondary>Align</secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <indexterm lang="it"><primary>Allinea</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="it">
    <primary>Strumenti</primary><secondary>Allinea</secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <figure>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">The Align tool in Toolbox</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Lo strumento di allineamento</phrase>
    </title>

    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject lang="en">
        <imagedata fileref="../images/toolbox/toolbox-align.png"
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="it">
        <imagedata fileref="../images/toolbox/it/toolbox-align.png"
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>

      <caption>
        <para lang="en">
          The Align tool is useful to align various image objects.
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          Lo strumento di allineamento serve ad allineare vari tipi di oggetti 
          nell'immagine.
        </para>
      </caption>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate Tool</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace nástroje</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Werkzeugaufruf</phrase>
      <phrase lang="es">Activación de la herramienta</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activation de l'outil</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Attivazione dello strumento</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Aktivering</phrase>
      <phrase lang="ru">Активизация инструмента</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">启动工具</phrase>
    </title>

    <para lang="en">You can activate the Align tool in several ways :</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          From the image-menu, through:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>T</accel>ools</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransform Tools</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>lign</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          Lo strumento di allineamento può essere richiamato tramite la
          voce di menù:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>S<accel>t</accel>rumenti</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>Strumenti di <accel>t</accel>rasformazione</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>llinea</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          By clicking on the tool icon:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          in the Toolbox,
        </para>
        <para lang="cs">
          Nástroj lze také vyvolat kliknutím na ikonu spreje v Panelu
          nástrojů:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          mit einem Mausklick auf das Symbol
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon> im Werkzeugfenster sowie
        </para>
        <para lang="es">
          La herramienta también puede activarse clicando en el icono:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          en cliquant sur l'icône de l'outil :
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon> dans la Boîte à Outils
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          Lo strumento può inoltre essere richiamato tramite la relativa
          icona:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          ved å klikke på symbolet
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          i verktøyskrinet
        </para>
        <para lang="ru">
          Инструмент также можно вызвать, нажав на пиктограмму:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          也可以通过点击工具图标：
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem lang="en;de;fr;it;no;ru">
        <para lang="en">
          By using the <keycap>Q</keycap> keyboard shortcut.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          über das Tastenkürzel <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          en utilisant le raccourci-clavier <keycap>Q</keycap>
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          O usando la scorciatoia da tastiera <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          eller med tastesnarvegen <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="ru">
          или с помощью клавиши быстрого доступа <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Key modifiers (Defaults)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Modifikační klávesy (výchozí)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Tastenkombinationen (Vorgabe-Einstellungen)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="es">Teclas modificadoras (por omisión)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Touches de contrôle (Par défaut)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Tasti modificatori (predefiniti)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Modustastane (Normalinnstillingane)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="ru">Клавиши-модификаторы (По умолчанию)</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">相关按键(默认值)</phrase>
    </title>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term lang="en">Shortcut</term>
        <term lang="cs">Zkratka</term>
        <term lang="de">Tastenkürzel</term>
        <term lang="es">Atajo del teclado</term>
        <term lang="fr">Touches de contrôle</term>
        <term lang="it">Scorciatoie</term>
        <term lang="no">Snarveg</term>
        <term lang="ru">клавиши быстрого доступа</term>
        <term lang="zh_CN">快捷键</term>

        <listitem>
          <para lang="en">
            The <keycap>Q</keycap> key will change the active tool to Align
            Tool.
          </para>
          <para lang="it">
            Il tasto <keycap>Q</keycap> cambia lo strumento attivo
            in "allinea".
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>
  </sect3>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Options</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Volby</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Eigenschaften</phrase>
      <phrase lang="es">Opciones</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Options</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Opzioni</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Verktøyinnstillingar</phrase>
      <phrase lang="ru">Параметры</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">选项</phrase>
    </title>

    <figure lang="en;it">
      <title>
        <phrase lang="en">Align options</phrase>
        <phrase lang="it">Opzioni di allinea</phrase>
      </title>

      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject lang="en">
          <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/tool-options-align.png'
            format="PNG" />
        </imageobject>
        <imageobject lang="it">
          <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/it/tool-options-align.png'
            format="PNG" />
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </figure>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term lang="en">Overview</term>
        <term lang="cs">Přehled</term>
        <term lang="de">Übersicht</term>
        <term lang="es">Descripción</term>
        <term lang="fr">Généralités</term>
        <term lang="it">Descrizione generale</term>
        <term lang="no">Oversyn</term>
        <term lang="ru">Общая информация</term>
        <term lang="zh_CN">概述</term>

        <listitem>
          <para lang="en">
            The available tool options can be accessed by double-clicking the
            align Tool icon.
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
          <para lang="cs">
            Volby nástroje jsou dostupné po dvojitém poklepání na ikonu spreje
            v Panelu nástrojů.
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
          <para lang="de">
            Die aktuellen Werkzeugeinstellungen für die Sprühpistole lassen
            sich durch einen Doppelklick auf das Symbol
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
            anzeigen.
          </para>
          <para lang="es">
            Las opciones disponibles para esta herramienta pueden ser
            accedidas realizando doble clic sobre su icono.
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
          <para lang="fr">
            On accède aux options de l'outil par un double clic sur l'icône de
            l'outil Aérographe
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>.
          </para>
          <para lang="it">
            Le opzioni relative allo strumento allinea possono essere raggiunte
            premendo due volte la sua icona.
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
          <para lang="no">
            Du får fram verktøyinnstillingane for sprøytepistolen ved å
            klikka på (eller i noen tilfelle dobbeltklikka på) symbolet
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png" />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon> i verktøyskrinet.
          </para>
          <para lang="ru">
            Чтобы вызвать параметры инструмента, нажмите дважды на пиктограмму
            инструмента.
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png" />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
          <para lang="zh_CN">
            双击喷枪工具图标可以看到可用的工具选项。
            <guiicon>
              <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata
                    fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align.png' />
                </imageobject>
              </inlinemediaobject>
            </guiicon>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry lang="en;it">
        <term lang="en">Relative to:</term>
        <term lang="it">Relativo a:</term>
        <listitem>
          <itemizedlist lang="en;it">

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>First item:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Primo elemento:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>Image:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Immagine:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>Selection:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Selezione:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>Active Layer:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Livello attivo:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>Active Channel:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Canale attivo:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            

            <listitem>
              <para lang="en">
                <guilabel>Active Path:</guilabel>
              </para>
              <para lang="it">
                <guilabel>Tracciato attivo:</guilabel>
              </para>
            </listitem>

          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <!-- FIXME: missing "Relative to" buttons and "Distribute" buttons -->

      <varlistentry>
        <term lang="en">Offset</term>
        <term lang="it">Scostamento</term>

        <listitem>
          <para lang="en">
            This entry controls the amount of displacement that could be 
            added to the desired alignment effect (in pixel). The value 
            could be posite and negative.
          </para>
          <para lang="it">
            Questa casella di inserimento accetta valori in pixel per lo 
            spostamento da aggiungere all'effetto di allineamento desiderato. 
            Il valore immesso può essere sia positivo che negativo.
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
